<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_000b0297-c288-4a50-aaa9-66e935203697" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="VIC"><sptc>E3P1</sptc><title id="_ba149561-a041-439f-8ffc-78b8e7b4d227">Roof drainage systems</title><archive-num>2019: FP1.1</archive-num><subclause id="_20fd5c15-1678-4efe-9eb9-5534943d5ef9" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e56bbc71-3f31-4919-8725-00ba97706a6b">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A roof drainage system must dispose of stormwater flows from rainfall events having an annual exceedance probability appropriate to:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_aac801cb-1829-4e68-9f64-9ef66c94f3e7">The importance of the building.</li><li id="_d9a5f947-a41d-4e5c-8013-b033dd04d9ff">The severity of potential damage to property, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_7de058b3-6859-45fc-b5c0-f4e66ea8eef9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">loss</xref> of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_2f655983-6c1d-44e4-8691-78462d05298d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref>, illness or injury that would result from the failure of the system.</li></ol></subclause></clause>